Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: This property is located at the intersection of I-94 & I-29 in Fargo and is one of the most visible locations in the market. Located in the main retail corridor of Fargo, there are 42 restaurants in a 1-mile radius and hundreds of retailers including the West Acres Mall, the biggest mall in the State of North Dakota.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located at the intersection of I-94 & I-29, this property features unbeatable visibility from the two main highways in North Dakota. This beautiful Class A office building has all the bells and whistles and can be divisible to a minimum of 4,000 SF.
This building includes a modern office layout with a good mix of private offices, small conference rooms, large conference rooms, open cubicle area, reception area, and meeting/banquet space with moveable walls for maximum flexibility.
